text: Ancita paravaricornis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1968. It is known from Australia.BioLib.cz - Ancita paravaricornis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Ancita Category:Beetles described in 1968
